            "title": "Evolution of Traditional Aerodynamic Variables in Bats (Mammalia: Chiroptera) within a Comprehensive Phylogenetic Framework",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Lucila I.",
                    "lastName": "Amador"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Francisca C.",
